[[!meta title="Sound and video"]]

Tails includes several sound and video applications:

  - [Audacity](http://audacity.sourceforge.net/) is a multi-track audio editor
    for Linux/Unix, MacOS and Windows. It is designed for easy recording,
    playing and editing of digital audio.
  - [Brasero](http://projects.gnome.org/brasero/)
  - [Pitivi](http://www.pitivi.org/)
  - [SoundJuicer](http://burtonini.com/blog/computers/sound-juicer)
  - Traverso

